Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report_...for_drv_fields(25.10)  timing_report_...for_drv_fields(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_drv_enable_ghz_notation_for_drv_fields

Syntax
       timing_report_drv_enable_ghz_notation_for_drv_fields {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  reporting  of  clock frequency in GigaHertz (Ghz). The default
       frequency unit is MegaHertz (MHz).

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

